nodes.title: 2) Models and Loras
widgets_values:
● Use any Flux checkpoint with the style you want for upscale.

● Use loras of the specific style of your image i.e. Realistic, toon, abstract ...etc

● Make a copy of lora stack and connect it in chain if need more than 3 loras.

nodes.title: 3) Controlnet
widgets_values:
●  Use Tile Controlnet here. 

● You can play with Strength and End percent. Lower values will change the image more.

nodes.title: 4)  Additional Prompt
widgets_values:
●  Use Addtional Prompts to further enhance your upscaling qaulity. 
●  You can add style prompts like realistic, anime, toon, etc...

nodes.title: SD Upscaler
widgets_values:
● If your image is getting seams visible, Then enable seamFix_mode in the SD upscaler node to - "Half tile + Intersections" 
- Set Lower Denoise value near 0.2-0.4 
- Also disable tiled decoding, You may run out of memory if you use low gpu pc
- Caution seamfix will increase the rendering time x3 times


● If you have GPU power and time, you can increase the sampling Steps to 20 or above to increase details.

● Do not put high denoise value, it will render distorted, smaller images.

nodes.title: Refining Notes
widgets_values:
● This Ksampler will give you a preview of how the upscaling is going to progress. 
  
● According to your selected Model, Loras and Prompts used, the image may slightly change from Original

● Use Euler,deis and Dpm_2 is seen to give best output. 

● Use Low Denoising (0.2 - 0.4) if major details are getting lost.

nodes.title: VL Upscale Prompt Guidance
widgets_values: Highres, sharp, detailed, great details, 4k, HD, 8k, best quality
Highres, sharp, detailed, great details, 4k, HD, 8k, best quality
